Description: # TOPPY - Graphical system rsources monitor in python
        
        Toppy is a graphical system resource monitor that uses matplotlib for plotting.
        
        Currently, displays 5 graphs:
        - CPU utilization
        - GPU utilization
        - Memory usage
        - Device IO
        - Network IO
        
        ## Installation
        
        `pip install toppy`
        
        ## Execution
        
        `python -m toppy`
        
